none.description:
{Mirth}

Increases Morale of target allied unit by +1.

While Mirth lasts, Morale penalties cannot reduce that unit below +1 Morale.

basic.description:
{Basic Mirth}

Increases Morale of target allied unit by +1.

While Mirth lasts, Morale penalties cannot reduce that unit below +1 Morale.

advanced.description:
{Advanced Mirth}

Increases Morale of target allied unit by +2.

While Mirth lasts, Morale penalties cannot reduce that unit below +2 Morale.

expert.description:
{Expert Mirth}

Increases Morale of all allied units by +2.

While Mirth lasts, Morale penalties cannot reduce affected units below +2 Morale.
